name: 过劳的爱丽丝Overworked Alice
description:
This is a precise platform game modeled after the King of Jumps



Alice: A newly graduated worker, is overloaded with work every day
In the process of working overtime, she experienced a magical journey...



The game is divided into 15 levels



Game system 1: 5 power jumps
Game System 2: Unable to adjust direction while jumping
Game System 3:
Useless super free jump (10 times per level) :

Players hit the wall during the jump can accumulate air slot → fill the air slot and then press the jump key → Automatically become a super jump that can adjust the flight direction by itself



OK, let's start our headache-like overtime experience!
